  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Neuropathic pain patient or patient with fibromyalgia

          -  Daily pain in more than 6 months

          -  Weekly average pain score 4 or more (VAS)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Treatment with antidepressants, anticonvulsants or any other pain medication except
             paracetamol

          -  Serious or unstable medical disease

          -  Prior or present diagnosis of mania, bipolar or psychotic disorder, delirium,
             suicidal, drug and alcohol dependence, severe agitation

          -  Patients who cannot cooperate and do not understand Danish
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
